  <div class="chapter-strip"><span class="label">Chapter 11</span><span class="name">Decision lifecycle</span></div>
  <h1>From signal to digest — a single decision's path</h1>

  <p>The DecisionStore (<code>decisions_store.py</code> + <code>state_db.Decisions</code>) is append-only and the canonical record of every accept and reject. <code>bot diagnose SYMBOL</code> reads from it; the daily digest summarises it; reconciliation reconciles fills against it.</p>

  {{ diagram("D7",
"sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant ST as Strategy / Lane
  participant OR as TradeOrchestrator
  participant RM as RiskManager
  participant AC as AlpacaClient
  participant DS as DecisionStore
  participant RC as Reconciler
  participant DG as Daily digest

  ST->>OR: Signal(side · entry · stop · TP · conviction)
  OR->>OR: build AuditObject<br/>(policy_version · strategy_version · regime)
  OR->>OR: ComplianceFlags + DataQualityFlags
  OR->>RM: check(order_request, RiskState)
  alt rule violated
    RM-->>OR: RiskRuleViolation(rule)
    OR->>DS: append(action='reject', reason=rule, audit, …)
  else allowed
    RM-->>OR: ok
    OR->>AC: place_order_with_stop_loss
    AC-->>OR: entry_id + stop_id
    OR->>DS: append(action='place', entry_order_id, stop_loss_order_id, audit, …)
  end
  loop 16:05 + 21:55 ET
    RC->>DS: read recent decisions
    RC->>AC: list_orders / positions
    RC->>DS: append(action='reconcile', notes)
  end
  DG->>DS: between(start_of_day, end_of_day)
  DG-->>DG: action_counts + top_rejection_reasons
  DG->>DG: send EOD email
",
"D7 — Decision lifecycle: every reject and every place is appended to the DecisionStore with full audit + compliance + data-quality JSON; reconciler and digest both read from the same store.") }}

  <h2>DecisionStore schema (state_db.Decisions)</h2>
  {{ table(
    ["Column", "Type", "What it stores"],
    [
      ["decision_id",            "string",   "<code>d_&lt;UTC&gt;_&lt;hex&gt;</code>"],
      ["timestamp_utc",          "datetime", "Decision time, UTC"],
      ["symbol",                 "string",   "Ticker / crypto pair / option underlying"],
      ["action",                 "string",   "<code>place</code> · <code>reject</code> · <code>reconcile</code> · <code>scale_in</code> · <code>exit</code>"],
      ["reason",                 "string",   "Human-readable reason (rule name on reject)"],
      ["strategy",               "string",   "<code>momentum</code> · <code>mean_reversion</code> · <code>breakout</code> · <code>wheel</code> · <code>news_trader</code>"],
      ["regime",                 "string",   "Live regime at decision time"],
      ["asset_class",            "string",   "<code>stocks</code> · <code>crypto</code> · <code>options</code>"],
      ["confidence",             "float",    "Lane conviction (0.0 – 1.0)"],
      ["expected_edge_bps",      "float",    "Strategy-estimated edge in basis points"],
      ["risk_after_json",        "json",     "VaR, gross, net, per-strategy halts after this trade"],
      ["compliance_json",        "json",     "Restricted-list hits, approved-venue check"],
      ["data_quality_json",      "json",     "Bar freshness, completeness, snapshot_id"],
      ["execution_constraints_json", "json", "Limits, time-stop, max slippage"],
      ["alerts_json",            "json",     "AlertEvents emitted for this decision"],
      ["audit_json",             "json",     "policy_version, strategy_version, regime, full inputs"],
      ["entry_order_id",         "string",   "Alpaca order ID (entry) on place"],
      ["stop_loss_order_id",     "string",   "Alpaca order ID (stop) on place"]
    ],
    ["18%", "10%", "72%"],
    compact=true) }}

  {{ callout("info", "Append-only by design",
     "<code>decisions_store.py</code> exposes only <code>append</code>, <code>recent</code>, <code>between</code>, <code>action_counts</code>, and <code>top_rejection_reasons</code>. There is no update or delete API — once a decision is recorded, it stays. This is what makes the diagnose tool, the digest, and the lab calibration loop trustworthy retrospectives.") }}
